Uses of Package
Catalano.Math

  • Packages that use Catalano.Math 
    Package Description
    Catalano.Imaging.Filters
    The Catalano.Imaging.Filters namespace contains collection classes, which provide different image processing filters.
    Catalano.Imaging.Tools
    The Catalano.Imaging.Tools namespace contains collection classes, which provide different image moments, analysis textures.
    Catalano.MachineLearning.Classification
    The Catalano.MachineLearning.Classification namespace contains interfaces and classes for classifications.
    Catalano.Math
    The Catalano.Math namespace contains set of math utilities, which are used by other Catalano framework's namespaces or may be used individually.
    Catalano.Math.Functions
    The Catalano.Math.Functions namespace contains set of functions as Normal, Gamma and others.
    Catalano.Math.Transforms
    The Catalano.Math.Transforms namespace contains set of transforms.
